Review Text: Loved the tirmasu jars...they were rich in taste. Very flexible and does a superb job for customised orders... Must try for gluten free stuff....

I have ordered for a Tiramisu jar which doesn't look like that and also spoilt. The baker has no idea how to make Tiramisu I'm wondering how it's so expensive when all they're giving is egg shells inside it and they didn't even use mascarpone cheese which is the basic ingredient to make Tiramisu instead they used malai(milk cream). I'd never recommend this place to anyone kindly be cautious!!!

Love the chocolate ganache cake. Beautifully crafted, delicious and such a pleasure on your palate. You just want to dig in for more. Thanks to the creator Pavni. You just added an extra magic making my daughter's first birthday even special.
Ordered red velvet jar they just sent jar not even giving spoon. Also red velvet cake is completely dried up.even the packed bottle is not hygiene

Loved the profiteroles... Loved the personalised cake she took order for with awesome decorations.... Give some notice and can expect some very exciting new options of deserts.
Must try for sure
Throughly enjoyed having Cheese cake,Banana bread and Energy bar.i highly recommend you try out this new venture. Service has been upto expectations
Super service and very good dishes. Our family definitely enjoyed the Brownies and cupcakes. We are now waiting to have a taste of yummy looking DEATH BY CHOICE
Love the red velvet cupcakes. Pineapple cakes are to die for. Loved their brownies n breads. By far the best cup cakes in the city . Recommend for the people looking for desserts
Best desserts ever. Love it!! The fresh fruit cake and the chocolate caramel is my favourite. Best is that they customise to our taste so order on!

Best cupcakes in Hyderabad, especially chocolate caramel and vanilla cupcakes! Don’t dare to order chocolate jars that will drool you away they are so rich in chocolate and is heavenly tasty! Just sit and order is what you have to do.
Sorry to say it!! But By far its the worst red velvet cake i have had. It tastes like a piece of bread with some colour in it, and the cheese from a different planet.
Awesome stuff by Deli-ciosa. Choco-chip Cookies are my fave! The cakes and energy bars are just out-of-the-world!!! Must try the gluten free stuff they make. One of the best in Hyd!!

Love the cheesecakes and cupcakes here. They also have energy bars which are super tasty and healthy at the same time. I have also tried the dessert jars and cookies and chocolate ganache is my favourite jar.

Delicious appetizers - have tried their Tomato & Mozzarella Bruschetta and Corn Tartlets with spicy bean salsa.  Perfectly done with the flavors subtle and just right.  Generous quantity too.Highly recommended.  Looking forward to trying out their desserts now.

I love love love the cakes and desserts, my favourite is the pineapple and fresh cream cake(customised) and the choclate strawberry cake is to die for. A perfect place for home made desserts made with love❤️

Some very yummy desserts....I have tried so many ,tiramisu,red velvet ,the energy bars ,gf cakes ,all were very good...it' definitely can add tag line of" noone can eat just one"...I promise you ,you LL go back for more...
And if you find that the restaurant is closed for many reasons ,you can always try your luck by calling +919052540222 and you will be pleasantly surprised.

Awesome desserts! Very authentic taste , brownies are to die for !
Cakes moist and amazing flavour yet not overpoweringly sweet .... just the right amount of sweetness!

Delectable desserts..some of the best deserts in the city!! Tried almost all of them..brownies, cheese cakes, muffins, etc., SPL mention for cheese cakes..unlike others who parade mouse as cheese cakes the cakes here taste authentic like new york cheese cakes..

The desserts are High on taste. Great presentation too. Would recommend their cakes. Wishing the team of deli ciaso all the very best. May they do exceedingly well so that we have more of their outlets around us. 
Best, 
Pooja
